Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
Csound is a cross-platform, user-programmable software synthesizer and sound
processing language of great power, with its own application programming
interface. csnd provides a Python interface to the Csound API.
info.name: csnd
info.summary: Python bindings for the Csound API.
